spec_data.Name: php-horde-Horde-Xml-Wbxml
spec_data.Description:
This package provides encoding and decoding of WBXML (Wireless Binary XML)
documents. WBXML is used in SyncML for transferring smaller amounts of data
with wireless devices.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 08:09:19 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Provides an API for encoding and decoding WBXML documents
